* I think this is a production that is easy for people who have never heard of 'KanColle' to enjoy and a production that is even more fun for those who've played the game. There are plenty of developments that you'll only see in the anime so if whilst enjoying each episode I'd be happy if you could be wondering, 'Will my favourite character make an appearance?' Even as an anime, please continue to support 'KanColle'!
